1928;;That Certain Thing;;American;;Frank Capra;;Viola Dana, Ralph Graves;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/That_Certain_Thing;;Molly Kelly (Viola Dana) intends to marry a millionaire. When she meets Andy Charles, Jr. (Ralph Graves), heir to a restaurant fortune, she sees her chance and marries him. Upon discovering the marriage, Andy's father (Burr McIntosh) becomes irate and disinherits his son. Andy attempts life as a ditch-digger to support his wife, but the results are not what he had hoped for.